                  "content": "ABOUT",
                  "y": 17
                },
                "U9OP6": {
                  "content": "The Best of Atlanta Comedy Showcase brings together the city's funniest stand-up comedians for one unforgettable night. Hosted at the iconic Laughing Skull Lounge in Buckhead, this monthly showcase features a rotating lineup of Atlanta's sharpest local talent alongside nationally touring headliners.\n\nWhether you're a comedy regular or looking for the perfect Saturday night out, this show delivers two hours of non-stop laughs in one of the Southeast's most beloved comedy venues. Doors open at 7:00 PM, show starts at 8:00 PM. Two-drink minimum applies.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "y": 48
